      "variant_note": "TPS62932=2A PFM SS-pin; TPS62933=3A PFM SS-pin; TPS62933F=3A FCCM SS-pin; TPS62933P=3A PFM PG-pin; TPS62933O=3A OOA PG-pin. All share same 8-pin SOT583 footprint."
    }
